UploadPolicy
public class FileByFileUploadPolicy
extends DefaultUploadPolicy

Specialization of DefaultUploadPolicy, where each upload HTTP request contains only one file.

This class :

  • Upload files without tranformation
  • File by file (uploading 5 files needs 5 HTTP request toward the server)
